2B50986D.Line7.EEB2B: I know they will come for me. Let them. We will have an army of the living and dead waiting for them.

5D732BE7.Line1.EEB2B: The Cathedral of Light has forsaken us! Our people starve and struggle, succumbing to the dangers of the swamp. Yesterday, my brother died, poisoned, after being bitten by a snake.

915C1EEB.Line5.EEB2B: Every letter and plea have gone unanswered by them. I gave them everything, but now all they shall have is my hatred.
